Package com.bumptech.glide.loader.model

Interface Summary
ModelLoader<T> An interface for translating an arbitrarily complex data model into a concrete data type that can be used by an StreamLoader to obtain an InputStream for an image represented by the model.
ModelLoaderFactory<T> An interface for creating a ModelLoader for a given model type.
 

Class Summary
Cache<A> A simple cache that can be used by ModelLoader and ModelLoaderFactory to cache some data for a given model, width and height.
FileLoader A simple model loader for File
FileLoader.Factory  
GenericLoaderFactory Maintain a map of model class to factory to retrieve a ModelLoaderFactory and/or a ModelLoader for a given model type.
ResourceLoader A model loader for handling resources.
ResourceLoader.Factory  
StringLoader A model loader for handling certain string models.
StringLoader.Factory  
UriLoader A model loader for trying to load Uris.
UriLoader.Factory  
UrlModelLoader<T> A base class for loading images over http/https.
